    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A widget that allows you to find, highlight and select boundaries (holes) in the mesh. To provide feedback during creation, it is necessary to specify a callback that will be called if a specific hole is selected. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
